</font><P><P><i></i></TD></TR><TR BGCOLOR=#666666><TD NOWRAP width=20% valign=top align=left><B><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=2><A HREF=http://pub3.ezboard.com/bpaladinsofnorrath.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=omenn>Omenn</A></FONT></B><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>Local user</FONT><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>(</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#FFFFFF>4/8/00</FONT> <FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#FFFFFF>10:10:40 am</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>)<BR></FONT><BR><img src=http://www.mxpx.cx/stuff/Omenn.jpg WIDTH=100 HEIGHT=219 ***></TD><TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=LEFT><B><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">Re: Depends...</font></B><HR><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">Oooo, self buffs!  *wiggles fingers in the air*  <br>
