Brell Serillis<P><i></i></TD></TR><TR BGCOLOR=#666666><TD NOWRAP width=20% valign=top align=left><B><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=2><A HREF=http://pub3.ezboard.com/bpaladinsofnorrath.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=amandal>Amandal</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/image/globalBlack.gif BORDER=0 WIDTH=10 HEIGHT=10></FONT></B><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>Local user</FONT><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>(</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#FFFFFF>4/8/00</FONT> <FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#FFFFFF>3:50:32 pm</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>)<BR></FONT></TD><TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=LEFT><B><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">Dueling... now this was funny</font></B><HR><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">I was at an event today where lots of dueling was taking place, high and low levels alike.<br>
